ChineseTraditional: 測試文字帶參數\n參數1 = <0>\n參數2 = <1>
ChineseSimplified: 测试文字带参数\n参数1 = <0>\n参数2 = <1>

English: Try to enter Key: Test1 or Test2 or Test3\nArgs: 111, 666\n and press the update button
ChineseTraditional: 試輸入Key: Test1 或 Test2 或 Test3\nArgs: 111, 666\n並按下更新按鈕
ChineseSimplified: 尝试输入Key: Test1 或 Test2 或 Test3\nArgs: 111, 666\n并按下更新按钮

English: Try to enter Key: Language or Win\n and press the update button
ChineseTraditional: 試輸入Key: Language 或 Win\n並按下更新按鈕
ChineseSimplified: 尝试输入Key: Language 或 Win\n并按下更新按钮

English: Below is TextMeshProUGUI\nlanguage fonts can be specified\nAvoid chinese characters not displayed
ChineseTraditional: 下方是TextMeshProUGUI\n可指定字體，並在切換語言時動態切換\n避免繁體或簡體無法顯示
ChineseSimplified: 下面是TextMeshProUGUI\n可指定字体，并在切换语言时动态切换\n避免繁体或简体无法显示
